title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VII Australia - now available
description:
It has been released: World Update VII Australia. In this video we will walk through the steps you need to take to install the latest World Update released by Asobo just 30 minutes ago.

0:00 intro
0:10 installing the update from the Store
1:50 starting MSFS 2020
2:55 install the second pair of updates
8:30 reviewing the initial changes
10:03 installing the optional updates
12:00 install the "real" world update
